trans-unit.source: Provides type conversion for the <xref href="System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Gir typekonvertering for den <xref href="System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: This converter exists primarily so that the existing `xml:lang` settings in an XML file do not interfere with the parsing of attributes that use <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage> as their underlying type.
trans-unit.target: Denne konverteringsprogram finnes primært slik at den eksisterende `xml:lang` innstillingene i en XML-fil vil ikke forstyrre analyse av attributter som bruker <xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage>som den underliggende typen.</xref:System.Windows.Markup.XmlLanguage>
